name: The Pines
description:
This is one of my favourite places, it's so calm and peaceful. It really quiets a racing mind, and the smell of fresh pine is intoxicating. An outtake from a new project I'm working on. Taken in December 2022 with a Fujifilm GFX50S II.

Free to claim from the 30th of December 2022 to the 6th of January 2023.
